\sum_{i=x}^{2x} 5 = 5 \cdot (2x - x) = 5x
\sum_{k=2x+1}^{5x+1} 5 = 5 \cdot (5x+1-2x-1) = 15x 
5x - 15x = -25
x = 25/10
x = 5/2
